---
title: Oyster Pork & Veggie Stir-Fry with Crushed Peanuts
description: Whip up a tasty bowl of quick-cooking pork strips tossed with colourful veggies and an easy sauce packed with umami flavours. It’s a takeaway standard made at home in a flash!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chinese-oyster-pork-veggie-stir-fry-b8815af7.jpg
